OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, "This is a landmark and a really big   
OL,6, step - a time to rejoice," said Father 
OL,7, Lee Taylor.                            
OL,9,FFather Lee and his partner Fabiano Da  
OL,10,FSilva Duarte have become what is       
OL,11,Fthought to be the first same-sex couple
OL,12,Fto be officially blessed by the Church 
OL,13,Fin Wales.                              
OL,15,FIt comes after the Church's governing  
OL,16,Fbody approved a new service of blessing
OL,17,Ffor same-sex couples in September.     
OL,19,FHowever it stopped short of allowing   
OL,20,Fgay couples to marry in its parishes.  
